#### New package name: __[iconsext](https://chocolatey.org/packages/iconsext)__

`iconsextract` has been deprecated because of Chocolatey [naming conventions](https://github.com/chocolatey/chocolatey/wiki/CreatePackages#naming-your-package).

It exists only for backward compatibility to provide a transitional dummy package for existing users and scripts which may still use this package ID.
